title: Terms and expressions neither defined in these Regulations nor defined in (I) and (II) above shall be interpreted with reference to the latest National Building Code in the relevant context
clause_text: Terms and expressions neither defined in these Regulations nor defined in (I) and (II) above shall be interpreted with reference to the latest National Building Code in the relevant context. “Access” means clear approach to a plot or a building.
